result:
div.padding-large
  div.flex.wide.justify-space-between
    //- :Left
    div: h2 Categories

    //- Right
    div: button(@click='$refs.newcategory.show()') New Category
  
  //- Contents
  table.wide
    tr
      td
        h3 Newborn Packages
        span Short Description
      td
        button.float-right Edit
    tr
      td
        h3 Newborn Packages
        span Short Description
      td
        button.float-right(@click='$refs.editcategory.show()') Edit

  modal(ref="newcategory" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.high-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding New Category
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            form.flex.column
              label Category Name
              input
              label Category Description
              textarea
              label Image
              input(type="file")
              label
                input(type='checkbox')
                span Active
              div
                button Cancel
                button Add Category

  modal(ref="editcategory" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.high-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding Edit Category
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            form.flex.column
              label Category Name
              input
              label Category Description
              textarea
              label Image
              input(type="file")
              label
                input(type='checkbox')
                span Active
              div
                button Delete
                button Update Category
